---
title: Chicken Banh Mi-Style Bowls with Pickled Carrots and Radishes
description: We've taken the traditional banh mi sandwich and turned it on its head! This quick and tasty meal has everything you love about the original, but packed into a satisfying dinner with fluffy jasmine rice. Spicy mayo, pickled veggies and saucy meat all come together for a Vietnamese-inspired party-in-a-bowl!
